\pard\f0\fs28 Subgen. {\b Chamaetia} Dumort. Creeping or procumbent shrubs. Leaves orbicular or ovate. Catkins usually on leafless peduncles arising from terminal buds of the previous year. Bracts concolorous. Stamens 2, free. Flowers with 1 or 2 nectaries.
